name: I threw the stick at the cat
name_original: I threw the stick at the cat
description:
Save the Cat! In Portuguese there is a song lullaby called "I threw the stick at the cat." In this game you need to save the cat!

"I threw the stick at the cat, but the cat did not die. Chica Lady was amazed at the roar that gave the cat. Miow"

This is the song lullaby that inspired this game. You need to dodge the thrown wood and survive.

Eating rats gives you life and the more extra time to catch, the more points you make.

Remember, cats have 7 lives. Know Funny Cat Art and Game in www.funnycat.com.br

Palete: Old School
